A 45-year-old man in Elgeyo Marakwet county has decided to go back to secondary school 26 years after posting a C- in the Kenya certificate of secondary education exams. Even though many expected Martin Kimosop to start planning for the future of his 3 children, the father of three decided to join form 2 at St Francis Kimuron in the county of Elgeyo Marakwet to pursue a journalism career.